===Etymology===
From {{bor|en|fr|accommodation}}, from {{der|en|la|accommodātiō||adjustment, accommodation, compliance}}, from {{m|la|accommodō||adapt, put in order}}. Superficially {{suffix|en|accommodate|ion}}. The sense of "lodging" was first attested in 1600.

